{"sections":{"product_breadcrumb_new_rCUd34":{"type":"Product-breadcrumb-new","settings":{"main_background_color":"#ffffff"}},"index_title_new_6pWaQ3":{"type":"Index-title-new","settings":{"main_background_color":"#ffffff","main_heading_text":"Learn More About KALKI Fashion’s Journey & Vision"}},"main":{"type":"Page-about-us-template-new","blocks":{"video_or_image_banner_QEcPX9":{"type":"video_or_image_banner","settings":{"youtube_video_id":"wopy0pAO_jo"}},"logo_with_small_texts_WzFFNh":{"type":"logo_with_small_texts","settings":{"main_small_logo_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/KALKI-ABOUT.svg","main_small_heading_text":"","main_small_information_text":"<p>Born in Mumbai, India in 2007, KALKI evokes the very spirit of the city it was founded in. An upstart, innovative, and dynamic brand – KALKI – offers the best of contemporary, ethnic Indian fashion and fusion-wear styles. Staying true to the brand’s unique promise of premium and wearable fashion, KALKI unveils fresh collections and all-new designs throughout the fashion calendar. KALKI’s design and aesthetic sensibility seek inspiration from all walks of life- be it the beauty of nature and heritage in art, architecture and culture, intricate creations, and the modern world to the home-bound handloom traditions of India.<\/p>"}},"heading_with_large_texts_TFybCD":{"type":"heading_with_large_texts","settings":{"main_large_heading_text":"Vision","main_large_information_text":"<p>To be a company that is a benchmark in the Indian fashion industry for its offerings and experiences.<\/p>"}},"logo_with_small_texts_PKKkYA":{"type":"logo_with_small_texts","settings":{"main_small_heading_text":"Mission","main_small_information_text":"<p>To be a preferred company of choice in Indian fashion globally for its delightful customer service, and quality product offerings by constantly evolving using innovation and design.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["video_or_image_banner_QEcPX9","logo_with_small_texts_WzFFNh","heading_with_large_text